<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8"/>
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge"/>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <title>ContEx Charts</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="<%= Routes.static_path(@conn, "/css/app.css") %>"/>
    <%= csrf_meta_tag() %>
  </head>
  <body>
      <section class="ctx-hero">
         <h1><img src="images/logo.png" height="30px"/> ContEx</h1>

        <p>A flexible charting library for Elixir server side charting.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="row">
        <h3>Sample charts written in a standard (non-live) view: (plus a sparkline &rarr;<%= sparkline([0, 5, 10, 15, 12, 12, 15, 14, 20, 14, 10, 15, 15]) %>)</h3>
      </section>
      <section class="row">
        <p>Refresh the page - the charts below will change...</p>
      </section>
      <section class="row">
        <article class="column">
            <%= make_a_basic_bar_chart() %>
        </article>
        <article class="column">
            <%= make_a_basic_point_plot() %>
        </article>
      </section>
      <section class="row">
        <article class="column">
            <%= make_a_basic_bar_chart2() %>
        </article>
        <article class="column">
            <%= ContexSampleWeb.GanttLive.build_ganttchart() %>
        </article>
      </section>

      <section class="row">
        <article class="column">
          <h2>LiveView Demos</h2>
          These below demos are all written as Phoenix LiveViews.
          <ul>
            <li>
              <%= link "Simple Bar Chart", to: Routes.live_path(@conn, ContexSampleWeb.BarChartLive) %>
              <p>Demonstrates the various options for <code>Contex.BarChart</code><p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <%= link "Bar Chart On Timer", to: Routes.live_path(@conn, ContexSampleWeb.BarChartTimer) %>
              <p>Shows <code>Contex.BarChart</code> getting updated server-side every 100ms<p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <%= link "Point Plot / Line Plot", to: Routes.live_path(@conn, ContexSampleWeb.PointPlotLive) %>
              <p>A simple <code>Contex.PointPlot</code> demo - also shows <code>Contex.LinePlot</code><p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <%= link "Sparkline", to: Routes.live_path(@conn, ContexSampleWeb.SparklineLive) %>
              <p>A simple <code>Contex.Sparkline</code> demo<p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <%= link "Gantt Chart", to: Routes.live_path(@conn, ContexSampleWeb.GanttLive) %>
              <p>A super simple <code>Contex.GanttChart</code> demo<p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <%= link "Pie Chart", to: Routes.live_path(@conn, ContexSampleWeb.PieChartLive) %>
              <p>A simple <code>Contex.PieChart</code> demo<p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <%= link "Simple Pie Chart", to: Routes.live_path(@conn, ContexSampleWeb.SimplePieChartLive) %>
              <p>A super simple <code>Contex.SimplePie</code> demo<p>
            </li>


          </ul>
        </article>
        <article class="column">
          <h2>Other Samples</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <%= link "Fun with Scales", to: Routes.live_path(@conn, ContexSampleWeb.ScalesLive) %>
            </li>
            <li>
              <%= link "Barchart in LiveComponent", to: Routes.live_path(@conn, ContexSampleWeb.MultiBarChart) %>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <h2>Resources</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <a href="/faq">FAQ</a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="https://hexdocs.pm/contex/Contex.html">Documentation</a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="https://github.com/mindok/contex">Source</a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="https://github.com/mindok/contex/blob/master/CHANGELOG.md">Changelog</a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </article>
      </section>
  </body>
</html>
